{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "12.1",
      "line_index": 12,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "255e86ab",
      "speaker": "アポロ",
      "ja": "着陸に成功いたしました。物資の調達を開始してください",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "19.1",
      "line_index": 19,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "f52169c1",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "ありがとう、アポロちゃん……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "24.1",
      "line_index": 24,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "cff534c",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "やれやれ、最新型の宇宙船であれば物資調達も自動に行うのですがね……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "27.1",
      "line_index": 27,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "6be1ff89",
      "speaker": "アポロ",
      "ja": "ワタシもアップグレードやプラグインを導入すれば機能の実装が可能です。無い物に目を向けず現実と向き合うことを推奨します",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "29.0",
      "line_index": 29,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b02bdb05",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "……言い争ってないで、早く済ませよう。ここの星に人はいなさそうなんだろ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "31.1",
      "line_index": 31,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "ca0f63d6",
      "speaker": "アポロ",
      "ja": "はい。文明的な建造物などの存在は確認できませんでした",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "33.1",
      "line_index": 33,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "3b09ffae",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "でも……動物とかはいるかもしれないから、気を付けて降りようね……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "49.1",
      "line_index": 49,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "9a034aca",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "うわあ……自然が豊かな星ね",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "51.1",
      "line_index": 51,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "12cd1d8a",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "ちょっと{G_PlayerName}くんの星と似てるかも……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "53.0",
      "line_index": 53,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "692d1403",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "確かに、そうだな",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "60.1",
      "line_index": 60,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "5fa2ff4",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "……！　何かが近づいてきます、注意を！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "75.1",
      "line_index": 75,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "65ec5657",
      "speaker": "魔獣",
      "ja": "グオオオオオッ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "89.0",
      "line_index": 89,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "15d8d613",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あ……あれって、俺を襲った魔獣！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "91.1",
      "line_index": 91,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "f02187d1",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "そんなことがあるわけがないでしょう、別の星なのですから！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "93.1",
      "line_index": 93,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "4114503",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "で、でも似てる……ね……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "95.1",
      "line_index": 95,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "b60f056",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "こんなところまで似てるの！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "103.0",
      "line_index": 103,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f14ced43",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "く、来るぞ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "105.1",
      "line_index": 105,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "d9685a12",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "迎え撃つわよ！",
      "zh": ""
    }
  ]
}
